#

Spicy Chickpea and Spinach Curry

30 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

IndianVegetarian

Course:

Main DishVegetarian

Tags:

QuickHealthyComfort Food

Description

A quick and flavorful chickpea and spinach curry with a kick of spice that warms the soul!

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • coconut milk: 1 cup
  • curry powder: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • onion (chopped): 1 medium
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • red pepper flakes (optional): 1 teaspoon
